  {
    "hotel_id": "5750371",
    "hotel_url": "https://www.agoda.com/rex-hanoi-hotel/hotel/hanoi-vn.html",
    "name": "Rex Hanoi Hotel",
    "detail": "My friends and I enjoyed a lovely stay of 3 nights at the Rex Hotel in Hanoi. The staff we very approachable, helpful, and professional and really helped to make our stay memorable. Special mention must go to Ms Angel on reception who was outstanding in terms of her knowledge, excellent English and helpfulness. Unfortunately, we had been caught in in the typhoon in Japan and so had to delay our arrival but Mr Lee (Sales Director) exercised some discretion which enabled us to reschedule our stay. The hotel is located in the old quarter - which is - as the title suggests not an pristine upmarket area - rather a more gritty environment - giving a real insight into the lives of the people living in Hanoi, I treasure such exposure but if you are looking for a more sanitised experience this is probably not the area for you. The hotel however is excellent. ",
